Plot twist ghê!

322
00:11:20,221 --> 00:11:23,475
Buongiorno~ Buongiorno~ (Xin chào)

323
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:26,603
Ơ? Ồ, xin chào ạ.

324
00:11:26,603 --> 00:11:27,437
Oa.

325
00:11:27,437 --> 00:11:28,563
